{
  "stem": "8947.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as I looked, you know, it was-- Bergen-Belsen was in a birch forest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I see these birch tree.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I love birch trees.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was so very desolate during, you know, the early spring.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it was April 15th, and I looked at that tree.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was close to me, but it looked like it was miles away because I could not move anymore.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I could see the buds, and those buds sprouted out of-- to me, life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes, you know, you have an unusual power that's given to you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't explain.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, we-- we are very, sometimes, very analytic and very reasonable.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think I can explain what force [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] descended up in me, what force encompassed me, that I was dragging, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had long fingernails, because they didn't give us anything to cut them, and I was putting my fingernails, and I was dragging myself.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just-- it wasn't far for me to the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I embrace its trunk, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I felt, oh, God has granted my wish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I-- am very emotional because I still feel how I felt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I embraced life for the last time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I looked up at the blue sky and asked why are we condemned to death we thought.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just because we are a Hebrew generation, that's why we are condemned to death and persecution.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I thought, well-- you know, I always try to be a positive person.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe I would be buried next to that tree.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And maybe I'd be a part of a root.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What an honor.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Still a form of life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I will be a part of a tree.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
